  "body_html": "<div class=\"top-bar\">\n            <div class=\"top-icon\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"6\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"6\"/><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"12\"/><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"18\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"18\"/></svg></div>\n            <div class=\"mode-toggle\">\n              <div class=\"mode-seg on-reg\">Regular</div>\n              <div class=\"mode-seg\">Fun</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"top-icon\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 20h9\"/><path d=\"M16.5 3.5a2.1 2.1 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4z\"/></svg></div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"convo\">\n            <div class=\"user-msg\">What's the latest reaction to the Grok 4 launch on X?</div>\n            <div class=\"assistant\">\n              <div class=\"glyph\"><span>G</span></div>\n              <div class=\"assistant-body\">Reaction has been strong over the last few hours. Developers are highlighting the reasoning gains, and a few posts call out the real-time data access as the differentiator<span class=\"cursor\">▍</span>\n                <div class=\"cite\">\n                  <div class=\"cite-head\">\n                    <div class=\"cite-av\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"cite-name\">Devin Park</div>\n                    <svg class=\"cite-verif\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 2l2.4 2.1 3.1-.5 1 3 2.9 1.4-1 3 1 3-2.9 1.4-1 3-3.1-.5L12 22l-2.4-2.1-3.1.5-1-3L2.6 16.4l1-3-1-3 2.9-1.4 1-3 3.1.5z\"/><polyline points=\"9,12 11,14 15,10\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#000\" stroke-width=\"2\"/></svg>\n                    <span class=\"cite-meta\">@devbuilds · 2h</span>\n                    <span class=\"cite-x\">𝕏</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"cite-text\">Grok 4's real-time X access is the actual moat here. Asked it about a thread from 10 minutes ago and it cited the exact posts.</div>\n                  <div class=\"cite-foot\">\n                    <span><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M21 11.5a8.4 8.4 0 0 1-8.5 8.5 8.5 8.5 0 0 1-3.6-.8L3 21l1.9-5.7A8.5 8.5 0 1 1 21 11.5z\"/></svg>128</span>\n                    <span><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><polyline points=\"17,1 21,5 17,9\"/><path d=\"M3 11V9a4 4 0 0 1 4-4h14\"/><polyline points=\"7,23 3,19 7,15\"/><path d=\"M21 13v2a4 4 0 0 1-4 4H3\"/></svg>342</span>\n                    <span><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M20.8 4.6a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.8 0L12 5.7l-1-1.1a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.8 7.8l1 1L12 21.2l7.8-7.8 1-1a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.8z\"/></svg>2.1K</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"prompt-zone\">\n            <div class=\"prompt-bar\">\n              <div class=\"prompt-clip\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M21.4 11.1l-9.2 9.2a5 5 0 0 1-7-7l9.1-9.2a3.3 3.3 0 0 1 4.7 4.7l-9.2 9.1a1.7 1.7 0 0 1-2.3-2.3l8.5-8.5\"/></svg></div>\n              <div class=\"prompt-input\">Ask Grok anything</div>\n              <button class=\"send-btn\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><line x1=\"12\" y1=\"19\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"5\"/><polyline points=\"5,12 12,5 19,12\"/></svg></button>\n            </div>\n          </div>",
